mitgutsch-fight.jpg.description: A man in grey clothing is located near the right edge of the image, waving a small white flag or surrender flag in an apparent act of surrender or defeat. He is standing amidst the chaotic scene, positioned in the lower right quadrant of the image.

whodoeswhat-city.jpg.description: A large brown cello is visible leaning against the entrance of the green house on the left side of the image. The instrument appears to be standing upright next to the doorway, and its distinctive curved body and neck are clearly visible against the building's exterior.

whodoeswhat-city2.jpg.description: A small saxophone can be seen in the bottom right portion of the image, being played by someone in black clothing who appears to be standing on the grass near the playground area. The instrument's golden brass color is visible against the green background.

whodoeswhat-city3.jpg.description: There is a yellow electrical box or utility container visible in the right portion of the image. It appears to be a small square or rectangular structure near a fence and some construction/delivery activity. The box is situated between what looks like a construction area and some greenery.

There is no clearly visible yellow electrical box in this illustration. While there are several vehicles and structures in the scene, including a yellow delivery van with what appears to be a pudding or cake logo on it, and some yellow construction equipment in the lower right, I cannot identify a specific yellow electrical box.

kf-f1.jpg.description: The F1 car appears as a small racing vehicle at the end of the winding racetrack. It's positioned near the waterfront in the right portion of the image, appearing to be painted in white and red colors. The car is shown from a side view, racing along the dark grey track that weaves through this colorful, Miami-style landscape. It seems to be in motion, suggested by its dynamic positioning on the track.

A Formula 1 racing car can be seen on the winding race track near the waterfront, in the middle-right portion of the image. The car appears to be white and red in color, racing along the grey track. It's positioned just before a curve in the track that leads to the beachfront area.

A Formula 1 racing car is visible on the winding race track near the water's edge, approximately two-thirds of the way through the track. The car appears to be white and red in color and is racing along the grey asphalt track bordered by blue water on one side.

A Formula 1 racing car is visible on the winding road track near the waterfront, in the right middle portion of the image. The car appears to be white and red in color, racing along the grey track. It's positioned just before a curve in the track that leads to the beach area.

The F1 car appears near the start of the winding race track at the top of the image. It is prominently displayed in red and blue colors, depicted as a racing helmet-shaped object. The car is positioned just after the 'START' line on the gray track, which is bordered by turquoise water features. It appears to be facing the direction of the race course that snakes through the illustrated cityscape.

A racing car is visible near the center-right of the image along the winding race track. It appears to be an F1-style race car in white and red colors, positioned at a curve in the track that runs along the waterfront. The car is heading towards the bottom right portion of the map-like illustration. It's drawn in a stylized, cartoon-like manner consistent with the rest of the illustration's aesthetic.

A Formula 1 racing car is prominently featured on the winding race track near the bottom-right portion of the image. The car appears to be white in color with racing livery and is positioned on a grey track section that curves along the coastline. The F1 car is depicted in motion, seemingly racing along the waterfront section of the track.

river-adventure-house.jpg.description: There is a small blue decorative whale water feature in the children's pool area on the right side of the image. It appears to be a plastic or concrete structure that children can play on or around. The whale is positioned in the smaller wading pool, separate from the main swimming pool with the yellow water slide. The whale is depicted in a playful, cartoonish style in a light blue color.

There is a decorative blue whale figure mounted at the top of the yellow water slide in the upper left portion of the image. It appears to be a cartoonish, smiling whale sculpture that serves as a decorative element for the pool's water slide feature. The whale is light blue in color and is positioned as if it's watching over the slide and swimming pool area.
